<scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
<head>Scope and Content
</head>
<p>Campbell County (Va.) Judgment Suit, 1798.  Consists of nine pages of court papers documenting arbitration of the court case Mickel vs. Hodges, which involved a financial dispute.  Papers include a summons, bond, memorandum, and award.  
</p>
